Its truly interesting how different life experiences can be for people,=20
even if  sharing the same technical diagnosis.
I currently have outspoken on one of the mac computers in my production=20
studio.
Its tied to a specific edition of pro tools, and the for me, needful=20
control  surface I use professionally.
I produce professional audio projects with this setup.  Speaking=20
personally, I could not work any other way.
Actually, I did not even get this copy of outspoken until well after 2005=
=20
too.
Again speaking personally the more respect for keeping broad solutions on=
=20
the  table, no matter the motivations making them needful the better.
Karen


